EXPECTED_RESULTS:
  Immediate_Benefits (First 24-48 hours):
    - Error Detection: 99%+ capture rate
    - Isolation: < 5 seconds to contain
    - Auto-Resolution: 60-80% of transient errors
    - User Impact: < 1% see error pages
    
  Short_Term (1-4 weeks):
    - Error Reduction: 40-60% fewer errors
    - Resolution Time: 50% faster fixes
    - Recurrence: 70% reduction in repeat errors
    - Code Quality: Measurable improvement
    
  Long_Term (3-6 months):
    - Error Rate: 80%+ reduction from baseline
    - Auto-Resolution: 90%+ of known errors
    - System Stability: 99.9%+ uptime
    - Technical Debt: Significantly reduced
